{"tid":475603,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲足協評選21世紀最強陣","createTime":"2017-11-21T09:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T15:18:49.000Z","uid":32938,"like":11,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"8da0e61c2788b2c6bcad22cb08e6a18556294849","tid":475603,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:18:19.000Z","msg":"下週，歐洲足協將揭曉本年度最佳陣容。今天他們評選出了本世紀以來的最佳陣容，美斯和C.朗拿度都在其中，有6名現役的皇馬和巴塞球員入選。<br />\n<br />\n　　這個陣容是按照進入21世紀以來入選年度最佳陣容的次數為標準，在各個位置上選出統治力強、巔峰時間長的球員。<br />\n<br />\n　　21世紀C.朗拿度曾11次入選歐洲足協的年度最佳陣容，而美斯則有8次入選，這兩名球員領銜鋒線，而另外一名入選的前鋒是亨利，職業生涯中他曾5次進入到年度最佳陣容。<br />\n<br />\n　　中場3人是沙維、恩尼斯達和謝拉特，而後衛線上，佩奧爾和比基坐鎮中堅，拿姆和拉莫斯分居左右。門將則是卡斯拿斯。<br />\n<br />\n　　按照目前效力或退役時效力的球隊來看，美斯、C.朗拿度、恩尼斯達、佩奧爾、比基、拉莫斯這6人都是皇馬和巴塞的球員。而亨利、卡斯拿斯、沙維也都曾是兩大豪門的重要球員，陣中沒有過皇馬巴塞效力經驗的只有拿姆和謝拉特。<br />\n<br />\n　　歐洲足協世紀最佳陣（括號內為入選年度最佳陣容次數）：<br />\n<br />\n　　門將：卡斯拿斯(6)；<br />\n<br />\n　　後衛：拉莫斯(6)，比基(5)，佩奧爾(6)，拿姆(5)；<br />\n<br />\n　　中場：謝拉特(3)，沙維(5)，恩尼斯達(6)；<br />\n<br />\n　　前鋒：C.朗拿度(11)，美斯(8)，亨利(5)。"},{"pid":"af14a6df52bb7f660138bd419ab9df1e53d597ae","tid":475603,"uid":141421,"like":30,"dislike":9,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"英超唯一謝拉特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1771b04f7bdd5c0abbf61b9c24558ce82e87c38","tid":475603,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"亨利退役個時響ny red bull wo  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a831fbebf39316c77be7fbc006e7f205361357","tid":475603,"uid":28151,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>亨利退役個時響ny red bull wo  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n按照目前效力或退役時效力的球隊來看，美斯、C.朗拿度、恩尼斯達、佩奧爾、比基、拉莫斯這6人都是皇馬和巴塞的球員。而<span style=\"color: red;\">亨利</span>、卡斯拿斯、沙維也都<span style=\"color: red;\">曾是</span>兩大豪門的重要球員，陣中沒有過皇馬巴塞效力經驗的只有拿姆和謝拉特。<br />\n<br />\n建議你驗驗眼先"},{"pid":"c8bcde40ecb77c2829bb14cdc5b627d50d30e82b","tid":475603,"uid":27785,"like":15,"dislike":10,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"其他冇問題，但謝拉德係21世紀最佳中場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40acc9ae2cd23c06b91540c4946ad7e2660392bd","tid":475603,"uid":141421,"like":13,"dislike":19,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他冇問題，但謝拉德係21世紀最佳中場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔敢話最佳 但絕對係最有代表性"},{"pid":"2980b16467284c6e9ed154b628ec7ee909d7f889","tid":475603,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"後衛無馬些路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78482e352914c560cd6a570fbdda92354cdf8946","tid":475603,"uid":7125,"like":42,"dislike":7,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其他冇問題，但謝拉德係21世紀最佳中場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔敢話最佳 但絕對係最有代表性</blockquote><br />\n果一冼直情係足球史上最有代表性既一冼啦"},{"pid":"5fc2ba9aaaefeeb8f0ac78dd89129dc8675d23f6","tid":475603,"uid":25086,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其他冇問題，但謝拉德係21世紀最佳中場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔敢話最佳 但絕對係最有代表性</blockquote><br />\n果一冼直情係足球史上最有代表性既一冼啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5574a4cce90d277c6cfb2323e48ba71f9f2e3c","tid":475603,"uid":25688,"like":18,"dislike":13,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:09:04.000Z","msg":"唔係話針對，猁狗謝老四英超世足歐足都未拎過，佢憑什麼做最佳中場？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我係擺到明針對"},{"pid":"f86c6333e9976f8af2ddb7c934db27b1655d1de3","tid":475603,"uid":59699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"謝4得碧咸都得啦咁"},{"pid":"b5321a8bf20c0deb1c81e4fe46d33c94adc68a62","tid":475603,"uid":37168,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話針對，猁狗謝老四英超世足歐足都未拎過，佢憑什麼做最佳中場？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我係擺到明針對</blockquote><br />\n係都林伯啦"},{"pid":"be2711c095cc071276b7cf1e2f27104a52823489","tid":475603,"uid":5549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"亨利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe3d94fb68f97e5f12b6e231994c6288c4e80fb","tid":475603,"uid":141421,"like":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其他冇問題，但謝拉德係21世紀最佳中場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔敢話最佳 但絕對係最有代表性</blockquote><br />\n果一冼直情係足球史上最有代表性既一冼啦</blockquote><br />\n有冇再煩d啊 次次都講"},{"pid":"4ba5a9e7c5f2801d5dda57fda2740a392d201aff","tid":475603,"uid":91152,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"歐戰20世紀英人BOX to BOX唔選謝仔選卡域克就最好喇"},{"pid":"fef9b2e40474ee4498114c4773290417fa75248a","tid":475603,"uid":581,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話針對，猁狗謝老四英超世足歐足都未拎過，佢憑什麼做最佳中場？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我係擺到明針對</blockquote><br />\n這個陣容是按照進入21世紀以來入選年度最佳陣容的次數為標準"},{"pid":"b263ebeec515f534ee7da2bde69ae502854d4889","tid":475603,"uid":581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:37:18.000Z","msg":"GOALKEEPER<br />\n<br />\nIker Casillas &ndash; 6 (2007, 08, 09, 10, 11, 12)<br />\nReal Madrid/Porto &amp; Spain<br />\nSpain's captain at UEFA EURO 2008 and 2012 also lifted the 2010 FIFA World Cup &ndash; three of the six times he made it into Team of the Year. Gianluigi Buffon (4 selections) and Manuel Neuer (3) are his main rivals for the No1 shirt.<br />\n<br />\nDEFENDERS<br />\n<br />\nCarles Puyol &ndash; 6 (2002, 05, 06, 08, 09, 10)<br />\nBarcelona &amp; Spain<br />\nEnjoyed a golden run from 2005 onwards, winning the UEFA Champions League with Bar&ccedil;a in 2006, 2009 and 2011, as well as UEFA EURO 2008 and the 2010 World Cup as a cornerstone of his country's defence.<br />\n<br />\nPhilipp Lahm &ndash; 5 (2006, 08, 12, 13, 14)<br />\nBayern M&uuml;nchen &amp; Germany<br />\nOne of Europe's most consistent performers of the past decade. Lahm's sequence of three successive Team of the Year appearances came to an end in 2015.<br />\n<br />\nSergio Ramos &ndash; 6 (2008, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16)<br />\nReal Madrid &amp; Spain<br />\nFive selections in a row are a measure of the Madrid man's standing, the defender having earlier been rewarded for his role in helping Spain to UEFA EURO 2008 glory. Will he make it six on the bounce this year?<br />\n<br />\nGerard Piqu&eacute;  &ndash; 5 (2010, 11, 12, 15, 16)<br />\nBarcelona &amp; Spain<br />\nNominated seven times in the last eight years &ndash; and picked on five of those occasions &ndash; Piqu&eacute; continues to be a hugely consistent performer for club and country.<br />\n<br />\nMIDFIELDERS<br />\n<br />\nXavi Hern&aacute;ndez &ndash; 5 (2008, 09, 10, 11, 12)<br />\nBarcelona &amp; Spain<br />\nThough a contender in 2005, it was not until his second involvement in 2008 that Xavi made the cut &ndash; then there was no dislodging him as unprecedented success with club and country kept him in the side five years running.<br />\n<br />\nAndr&eacute;s Iniesta &ndash; 6 (2009, 10, 11, 12, 15, 16)<br />\nBarcelona &amp; Spain<br />\nLike midfield partner Xavi, once he forced his way into Team of the Year Iniesta proved impossible to displace until 2013; he also returned in splendour in 2015 and kept his spot last year.<br />\n<br />\nSteven Gerrard &ndash; 3 (2005, 06, 07)<br />\nLiverpool &amp; England<br />\nOne of five midfielders selected three times. However, seven nominations were key to taking Liverpool's talisman into the ultimate XI at the expense of Kak&aacute; (five nominations), Ronaldinho (four), Pavel Nedvěd (three) and Zin&eacute;dine Zidane (three).<br />\n<br />\nFORWARDS<br />\n<br />\nCristiano Ronaldo &ndash; 11 (2004, 07, 08, 09, 10, 11, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16)<br />\nManchester United/Real Madrid &amp; Portugal<br />\nNominated a record 13 times, the Portuguese phenomenon has been included in the Team of the Year on no fewer than 11 occasions, three more than any other player. The 2016 team marked his tenth appearance on the spin.<br />\n<br />\nLionel Messi &ndash; 8 (2008, 09, 10, 11, 12, 14, 15, 16)<br />\nBarcelona &amp; Argentina<br />\nLike Ronaldo, Messi was initially categorised as a midfielder &ndash; collecting the first of 11 consecutive nominations in 2006 &ndash; and has missed the Team of the Year cut just once, in 2013, since his 2008 debut.<br />\n<br />\nThierry Henry &ndash; 5 (2001, 02, 03, 04, 06)<br />\nArsenal &amp; France<br />\nA candidate in the first six editions of the vote. Henry's consistency was such that he got into the final selection five times, including the first four &ndash; the only player to achieve that."},{"pid":"11941e1061e7a951f899d8cd9158067cf03d0cd2","tid":475603,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"pique <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521341f8e38050ee1d866f8eca3c0cb909f07c66","tid":475603,"uid":5191,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"謝拉特憑咩牙<br />\n入得多就得算乜標準<br />\n禾地暴聯d人都先係最強"},{"pid":"b3c4f6c50c26441a2be717dcbfb7cbcb212ce1a7","tid":475603,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝拉特憑咩牙<br />\n入得多就得算乜標準<br />\n禾地暴聯d人都先係最強</blockquote><br />\n同亨利黃金連攜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.